{"tid":1370052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[強烈建議］今日元朗盡量保留輕鐵路綫","createTime":"2019-07-27T01:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T02:08:04.000Z","uid":263016,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e9d4263fb8623426c0e0d09a579146577e9e3499","tid":1370052,"uid":263016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:02:07.000Z","msg":"啱啱開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日盡量保住條輕鐵路線，呢個方便be water之餘仲令人感到我哋真係好和平。其實最主要都係方便俾人閃，西鐵分分鐘唔停朗屏同元朗又冇巴士。<br />\n<br />\n但係我相信黃昏左右黑黑一定會整停輕鐵，令我哋被圍！所以入黑前一定要散，今日緊記，唔好硬並，一定要be water！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8471bafdd2b94abbfc22ac468c35cf55462f4a","tid":1370052,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:21:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>各位手足<br />\n萬事小心<br />\n<br />\n#一個都不能少<br />\n#727</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"bf5d19692bd67b3ca02309fc46b8e62ec15140ca","tid":1370052,"uid":271782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:24:35.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n只怕警方要求港鐵不停元朗站及朗屏站"},{"pid":"02e202c658293946db93cf6b5ac331f7ce73915e","tid":1370052,"uid":1544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:29:42.000Z","msg":"本身條路都窄 <br />\n唔行輕鐵條路實迫到水泄不通"},{"pid":"f5d9b95827ea3e2684744d2044cb3e2223153e1f","tid":1370052,"uid":187082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf5d19692bd67b3ca02309fc46b8e62ec15140ca","tid":1370052,"uid":271782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:24:35.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n只怕警方要求港鐵不停元朗站及朗屏站"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:08:04.000Z","msg":"所有經元朗嘅巴士都會經山水樓之後直接上公路"}]}